{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"91aa342346","title":"关于鼓励士气争取大胜致彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"90c2b4ff75","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"91aa342346"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"84a8b3ae89","type":"title","text":"关于鼓励士气争取大胜致彭德怀等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346"},{"id":"ed811e7619","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、邓、朴、洪，并告宋、陶，高、贺","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346"},{"id":"195619ddd9","type":"paragraph","text":"你们十一月廿八日午时给西线各军电及同日十五时给九兵团电均是很正确的。此次是我军大举歼敌根本解决朝鲜问题的极好时机，西线争取好灭五个美英师及四个南【朝】鲜师，东线争取歼灭两个美国师及一个南（朝】鲜师，是完全可能的。整个战役准备打廿天左右，分为许多个大小作战，中间包括几次小休整，每次少者一天二天，多者三天四天，整顿队势，接着再打，这样就全体说来，轴性反会比较少一些，比较更节省些。望你们鼓励士气，争取大胜。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346"},{"id":"0bd0e3a375","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346"},{"id":"4a1021702d","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿八日廿四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346"},{"id":"e5f5e7376a","type":"paragraph","text":"1宋，指宋时轮，当时任中国人民志愿军第九兵团司令员兼政治委员。陶，指陶剪，当时任中国人民志愿军第九兵团副司令员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346"}],"page":{"id":"097cb5231a","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"91aa342346","start":395,"end":395}}}},"__N_SSG":true}